---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-24 pb-32 md:pt-32">
  <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Business and tech optimization</p>

  <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-4xl font-display text-5xl leading-[1.05] tracking-tight md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl">
    We find the drag in your operations, and we remove it.
  </h1>

  <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-muted md:text-xl">
    Slow processes. Expensive cloud bills. Data stuck in five places. Manual work that shouldn&rsquo;t be manual. We audit the mess, write a plain-English plan, and ship the fix.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
    <Button href="/contact" size="lg">Book a call</Button>
    <Button href="/services" variant="secondary" size="lg">See our services</Button>
  </div>
</section>
